        "content": "<p>I have settled up a zulip server to complement, discuss, and extend the content of the webpage <a href=\"https://agrothendieck.github.io/\">Thèmes pour une harmonie</a> on A. Grothendieck. The webpage contains letters, a particular classification of Grothendieck's works (the themes),  published and unpublished works, projects of transcription, translations, and more. Get involved in a community! <a href=\"https://grothendieckthemes.zulipchat.com/join/kma55hxjnfm52xyy3wc3pkf7/\">https://grothendieckthemes.zulipchat.com/join/kma55hxjnfm52xyy3wc3pkf7/</a></p>",
