        "content": "<p>I am currently working (in particular for the interest of the category theory community) on a transcription of H X Sinh’s thesis <a href=\"https://agrothendieck.github.io/picardbrauer/GCS.pdf\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>G</mi><mi>r</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">Gr</annotation></semantics></math></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"katex-html\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">G</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">r</span></span></span></span>-catégories</a> (via <a href=\"https://pnp.mathematik.uni-stuttgart.de/lexmath/kuenzer/sinh.html\">link</a>).</p>",
